      <title>成本拖累盈利，Canaccord 股价创一年来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/canaccord-s-expansion-costs-offset-record-wealth-segment-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于招聘和技术投资成本上升，加通社报道，Canaccord Genuity Group Inc. 的盈利不及预期，掩盖了其财富管理部门创纪录的收入，导致其股价出现一年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/canaccord-s-expansion-costs-offset-record-wealth-segment-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
